    <!-- ── Character Builder ────────────────────────────── -->

    <h2 id="builder">Character Builder</h2>

    <p>
      An interactive form that walks you through character creation. Click
      attributes to set them, pick skills from dropdowns with auto-calculated
      targets, select your casting path and spells, and fill in weapons, armor,
      society details, and contacts. Everything prints as a formatted two-page
      character sheet.
    </p>

    <table>
      <tr><th>Feature</th><th>What It Does</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Attributes</td><td>Click &minus;3 to +3 for each stat; derived values update live</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Skills</td><td>Pick from all skills; stat, target, and pool budget calculated automatically</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Station</td><td>Set your economic position (0&ndash;5); affects what gear you can start with</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Magic</td><td>Choose Scholarly (pick individual spells) or Wild (select your schools, get all spells)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Equipment</td><td>Type in weapons, armor, and inventory; soak and hinder auto-totaled</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Society</td><td>Record Backing rating, Ledger state, patron, and charter</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Print</td><td>Generates a clean two-page sheet matching the blank template</td></tr>
    </table>

    <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
      <a href="tools/character-builder.html" style="color: var(--aether); font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1rem;">
