    </p>

    <!-- ── Blank Sheet ──────────────────────────────────── -->

    <h2 id="blank-sheet">Blank Printable Sheet</h2>

    <p>
      A two-page printable character sheet with all the fields you need.
      Open it in your browser and use Print or &ldquo;Save as PDF&rdquo; to
      get a clean blank sheet ready to fill in by hand.
    </p>

    <table>
      <tr><th>Page</th><th>Contents</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Page 1</td><td>Identity, Station, attributes, weapons, armor, character description, skills, XP, wound &amp; exhaustion tracks</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Page 2</td><td>Magic, spells, inventory, adventuring society (Backing, Ledger), faction, contacts, backlash effects, notes</td></tr>
    </table>

